cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CR 

This paper is about a benchmarking framework for learning in federated settings. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses challenges in the machine learning pipeline and proposes a benchmarking framework for learning. The second likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as federated learning involves distributed computing. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper discusses learning models to improve user experience. The fourth likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the paper discusses federated networks such as autonomous vehicles. The fifth likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as federated learning involves privacy and security concerns.
